Title: An Act Changing the Name of Caridad Elementary School in Barangay Bagroy in the City of Bago to Perez-Poblete Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 740
An Act Changing the Name of Caridad Elementary School in Barangay Bagroy in the City of Bago to Perez-Poblete Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Caridad Elementary School in Barangay Bagroy, in the City of Bago, is hereby changed to Perez-Poblete Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
